title: Maine Dhundha Ye Sara Jaha
content:
(Chorus)
Maine Dhundha Ye Sara Jahan,
Tere Jaisa Na Koi Mila – 2
Jaise Tune Kiya Hai Kshama,
Tere Jaisa Na Koi Mila – 2
Maine Dhundha Ye Sara Jahan,
Tere Jaisa Na Koi Mila

(1)
Paapo Ka Tha Karz Mujhpe Jo Bhari,
Dukho Me Zindagi Guzari Thi Saari

Mere Gunaho Se Mujhko Bachane,
Tune Khuda Apni Zindagi Thi Wari – 2
